name: ProtectiveLocator
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: protective locator
des: Get the location and directions to conference rooms on the main campus of Protective Life in Birmingham, Alabama. Invoke the skill by saying 'Ask Protective Locator to find the XYZ conference room', where XYZ is the name of the conference room you need to find. You can also obtain directions to the conference rooms.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
